
This directory contains subdirectories with different models and interfaces
provided with BAT.

Interfaces:
-----------

 * RooInterface
   - interface allowing to run BAT on a problem/data defined in a
     standard RooFit workspace format, requires ROOT 5.24 or later
   - provided by Gregory Schott <gregory.schott@cern.ch>

* StackModel
   - a model for fitting a "data histogram" to a set of "pdf histograms". 
   - see the tutorial on hypothesis testing for details 
   - provided by Kevin Kroeninger <kevin.kroeninger@cern.ch> 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
More models and interfaces will be added in the future.

